Big Brother Naija season 2 star, Bassey Ekpeyong has quietly married beautiful Nadia Ann. The ebony and ivory couple have been dating quietly for a little over a year and decided to sign the dotted lines when their love needed to go to the next level. The quiet wedding was held in Detroit on the 6th day of December, 2019.  Bassey relocated about a month ago to the US to join Nadia who is based in the US but shuttles Nigeria and is friends with many Nigerian celebrities. Bassey has been receiving tons of congratulations from his former fellow housemates on his Instagram handle. Congratulations to Nadia and Bassey.